# FILE: studentDashboard/learningVault/myBookmarks.desc
# ROLE: Personal Knowledge Repository
# ROUTE: /dashboard/bookmarks (future route)
# ACCOUNT: Student only
# THEME: Dark · organized archive · tag-based

## 1. FILTER ROW
- TABS: [📚 الكل] [📝 ملخصات] [🧪 امتحانات] [🎓 دورات أكاديمية]
- SEARCH: real-time input · bg-[#0F1828] · border-[#1E2D45]
- SORT: 📅 الأحدث · 🔠 أبجدي · 📂 حسب الكلية

## 2. BOOKMARKED RESOURCE GRID
- GRID: grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 · gap-5
- CARD STYLE: bg-[#0F1828] · border border-[#1E2D45] · rounded-2xl
- CARD COMPONENTS:
  - TYPE ICON: PDF icon / Play icon (matching content type)
  - TITLE: "تحليل الإنشاءات II — محلولة 2025"
  - METADATA: "الكلية: مدني · السنة: 3" — muted small text
  - ONE-CLICK READ: button → opens directly in /library/viewer/:id

## 3. COLLECTIONS (Folders)
- Custom groups: [✍️ الامتحان النهائي] [📖 ملخصات النصف]
- Drag-and-drop (or add-to-collection button on each card)

## 4. ACADEMY PROGRESS SYNC
- For bookmarked courses: small progress bar on card
- "Progress: 65%" + [▶️ متابعة الدرس] → /academy/course/:id

## 5. CONTRIBUTION NODE
- If student uploaded approved content: "أضفت 12 مصدراً للمجتمع"
- XP earned from contributions: "+600 XP" — emerald text

## 6. ACTION BAR
- [🗑️ حذف المحدد] [📥 تحميل كـ CSV]
- Footer: "محفوظاتك متزامنة — Challenge Every Day."
